    failed with "Unknown merge tool" because they were never registered).

    - Extract the shared content-hardening core (has-checks, the fatal flag,
      Unicode/Trojan-Source surfacing, fail-closed git_review_finish, cleanup) into
      git-review-scan.sh, sourced by the existing git-review-driver.sh
