      difftool.review-{meld,kdiff3,diff} and mergetool.review-{meld,kdiff3}
      (include it from ~/.gitconfig to activate).
    - Fix a latent binary-detection bug: 'grep --perl-regexp \x00' needs '--text',
      else GNU grep's binary heuristic short-circuits, a NUL is not matched, and a
      binary blob is misclassified as text and opened in the viewer. Fixed in both
      git-review-scan.sh and git-review-driver.sh.

