Author: claude (dev22 c20093f1-1b30-4397-87b6-9586321c87df) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Tue Jun 30 19:26:02 2026 -0400

    dm-prepare-release: document bindmounts space-handling

    pbuilder word-splits BINDMOUNTS internally, so a bind-mount path with a space is
    unsupported by pbuilder itself and a bash array would not help; note that the
    space-joined string is the expected form (the build paths have no spaces).

