Author: claude (dev22 c20093f1-1b30-4397-87b6-9586321c87df) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Tue Jun 30 18:42:41 2026 -0400

    dm-check-unicode: default HELPER_SCRIPTS_PATH via '[ -v ] ||'

    Use the preferred defaulting idiom '[ -v HELPER_SCRIPTS_PATH ] ||
    HELPER_SCRIPTS_PATH=...' instead of '"${HELPER_SCRIPTS_PATH:-...}"': it defaults
    only when the name is unset, so an explicitly set-but-empty value is respected,
    and it reads as a one-time set-at-source statement.

