    dm-packaging-helper-script: make --batch/--no-batch mandatory, share machinery

    Background: batch mode and --no-batch took divergent paths. Batch set
    project_name/website/changelog/path/remote_list per iteration and ran
    post_run_hook_list afterward; --no-batch only set
    batch_current_package_reponame from $(basename "$PWD") and called the
