      case / if) -> 1 line calling dm-consumer-load.sh. Gate step
      (was 10 inline lines) -> 1 line calling canonical-repos-gate.sh.
    - reusable-cppcheck.yml: Load step (was 38 inline lines) ->
      1 line. dmf checkout moved to the top (was if: always at the
      end; now needed up front for ci/ helpers).
    - reusable-codeql.yml: Load step (was 53 inline lines, with the
      conditional build-mode logic) -> 1 line calling
      codeql-load-config.sh. dmf checkout moved to the top.

    Net: -188 / +41 lines in the three workflow YAML files. ~150 lines
    of bash moved from YAML-embedded to .sh files where shellcheck
    sees them.

