    agents: shrink CLAUDE.md to 1-line redirect; restructure AGENTS.md

    CLAUDE.md was 20 lines after the previous session expanded it to
    explain the gate inline. AI sessions historically skip CLAUDE.md
    even when it's short (the original 'See AGENTS.md' redirect went
    unread); making it longer didn't help. Try the inverse: make
    CLAUDE.md a single sentence that pairs the imperative with the
    consequence ('CI enforces what it documents'). The cost of being
    wrong about adherence is bounded -- if AI still skips it, CI
    catches the violations and forces a force-push cycle.

