    scorecard FP doc: document Signed-Releases as deliberate inconclusive

    Verified across 500+ repos in the four namespaces (org-ai-assisted,
    Kicksecure, Whonix, adrelanos): zero GitHub Release objects have
    ever been created. Tags only.

    Scorecard's Signed-Releases therefore returns -1 / inconclusive on
    every repo and is excluded from the aggregate score - this is the
    desired state given the offline-key threat model.

