commit 16659a92e11439ec6969e46cec7f54856ce93c79
Author: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date:   Fri May 8 15:21:18 2026 +0000

    claude-code: drop id-token: write

    The reusable workflow no longer needs id-token: write (the action
    authenticates to api.anthropic.com via a static ANTHROPIC_API_KEY;
    OIDC federation is unused). Drop the permission to honor
