    dm-github-personal-policy: parse flags after the username

    Codex P1 review of 60c263c: the parser broke at the first positional
    arg, so 'dm-github-personal-policy <user> --dry-run' silently ran in
    APPLY mode (--dry-run treated as ignored extra) and mutated repo
