        test_set_fork_approval_user_refused.sh removed alongside the
        binary; the shellcheck-clean file list dropped the entry. The
        User-account refusal path the latter test exercised is still
        covered indirectly via ghorg_account_type's exposure through
        ghorg_list_repos / github-org-fork / github-org-clone.

