    dm-reprepro-wrapper: drop pre-call debug logs that broke under set -u

    main() referenced make_reprepro_codename_item before
    set_dist_build_reprepro_folder_options had a chance to default it,
    producing "unbound variable" under set -o nounset. The variable is
    defaulted (via [[ -v var ]] || var=...) inside the function call on
    the next line, so the pre-call "before:" log lines were both
    redundant and broken; the matching "after:" lines are removed for
    symmetry.
    https://claude.ai/code/session_01BAQS9pE9zQYieV6Uys9Reo

